Enumerations

Detailed Description

The section has a list of all internal data structures which are used internally by the SOC module.

Typedef Documentation

typedef struct SOC_MCB_t SOC_DriverMCB

SOC Master Control Block.

The structure describes the SOC Driver and is used to hold the relevant information with respect to the SOC module.

typedef struct SOC_HwAttrib_t SOC_HwAttrib

SOC Hardware Atrributes.

SOC Driver Hardware Attributes which allow the driver to be ported to different SOC. This is an internal structure and is not exposed or configurable by the applications.

typedef struct SOC_SysInterrupt_t SOC_SysInterrupt

SOC System Interrupt.

The structure describes the mapping of the system interrupt to a corresponding ISR.

typedef struct SOC_SysInterruptListener_t SOC_SysInterruptListener

SOC System Interrupt Listener.

The structure defines a listener block which is listening and needs to be notified on the system interrupt.

typedef enum SOC_TranslateAddr_LUT_Type_e SOC_TranslateAddr_LUT_Type

Enumeration for address translation lookup table.

The enumeration describes the direction of address translation.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum SOC_TranslateAddr_LUT_Type_e

Enumeration for address translation lookup table.

The enumeration describes the direction of address translation.

Enumerator
